	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>A radiant servant blasts their enemies with light and protects their allies. Most radiant servants have formed a pact with an angel or other &amp;reference[celestial], who typically give power to their warlocks for benevolent reasons. Most who serve celestials and their causes become paladins, but radiant servants have a personal pact, becoming avenging angels of radiant power.</em></p><table><caption><p>The Radiant Servant</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Features</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>1</p></td><td><p>Bonus Cantrip: <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.e4MmHYtpD4jFrRuH]{Light}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.A4UCL7CST8SHyeOC]{Imbue Light},</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>6</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.8evXHUkCY6ct94KP]{Guardian Angel}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>10</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.NdHczaThZnu60ip0]{Heavenly Aspect}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>14</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.s2wzUp7CLTkhccWc]{Radiant Conflagration}</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table><caption><p>Expanded Spell List</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p><strong>Warlock Level</strong></p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p><strong>Extra Spells</strong></p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>1</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.Z7kTdTSJzi68e588]{Divine Favor}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.HKiFSQzi9E2rgaLV]{Healing Word}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.c9SfIJndbbCZK2Le]{Aid}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.gQCBKxTyZeqCvy0D]{Lesser Restoration}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>5</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.Y9ujzi4f01yflTyj]{Beacon of Hope}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.cZLKEokFoqKN8dqR]{Mass Healing Word}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>7</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.3Dpyp708Lxvq4niO]{Death Ward}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.r6JonKXqYZK8gTaM]{Guardian of Faith}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>9</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.qSuF4WJzTahI6hNO]{Flame Strike}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.Mi4qWwfmDYv6GrkI]{Greater Restoration}</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table>",
